Changelog for Usermin::Vacation

Version 0.9
- Rolled in a patch from Colin Hill at Duke University that allows
  the user to update their vacation message without cycling vacation
	on and off. Colin's patch also fixed the problem where user's couldn't
	update their from: line. Thanks Colin!

- Implemented an RFE from Hank Mensinga to have vacation determine
  the hostname from the URL for virtual hosting enviroments.

Version 0.5 
- Added German translation contributed by Danny Trommer (dantro@esc.de)
